<cell type="page">550</cell><cell><row xml:id="txtcmnt-550-01"><cell type="data-term">Phantasus</cell><cell type="data-definition">hos den romerske digter Ovid (43 f.Kr.-17 e.Kr.) en af drømmeguderne, der tager skikkelse af alle mulige genstande (<hi rend="italic">Metamorfoser</hi>, 11, 641 ff.).</cell></row><row xml:id="txtcmnt-550-02"><cell type="data-term">La Storta</cell><cell type="data-definition">by nord for Rom.</cell></row><row xml:id="txtcmnt-550-03"><cell type="data-term">Gensdarm</cell><cell type="data-definition">politisoldat.</cell></row></cell>
